A yet-to-be-identified young man has been killed by a stray bullet allegedly fired by police officers in Festac area of Lagos State.
It was gathered that the unfortunate incident occurred on Monday afternoon, July 25, 2022.
Details of the incident are still sketchy, but according to an eyewitness, the police officers were trying to seize some bikes when they suddenly opened f%re.
A stray bullet reportedly hit the victim, killing him on the spot.
 
